{"title":"歌唱总路线","authors":["柯仲平","靳以","方纪","梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱总路线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线上人六亿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柯仲平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线上人六亿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催开战马比高低，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人有共产主义英雄劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马有多快好省四只蹄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一鼓劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跑出二万五千里；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加鞭再加鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把英国美国都抛在后边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席，年六十，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“万里长江横渡”当休息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风完全压倒西风时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们跟着毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞭一扬，飞上天河游泳去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你该干些什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靳以"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一个五年计划你干了些什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第二个五年计划你想干些什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志，每天都要问自己。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设社会主义祖国人人有责！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日出东方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方纪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方升起红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光芒万丈照四方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昆仑山上望一望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西方黑来东方亮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指路碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一部“八大”文件——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座指路碑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着它的红线走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺着它的箭头飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天就顶二十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路远何足畏！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天十万八千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直把英国追！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}